# Environment Configuration Template

# Copy this file to create your actual configuration
# DO NOT commit files with actual credentials to version control

## Clerk Configuration
CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_your_key_here
CLERK_JWT_ISSUER_DOMAIN=your-app.clerk.accounts.dev

## Convex Configuration  
CONVEX_DEPLOYMENT_URL=https://your-deployment.convex.cloud

## Instructions:
# 1. Replace the placeholder values above with your actual credentials
# 2. Update utils/auth.js with CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY
# 3. Update utils/convex-client.js with CONVEX_DEPLOYMENT_URL
# 4. In Convex dashboard, set CLERK_JWT_ISSUER_DOMAIN via:
#    npx convex env set CLERK_JWT_ISSUER_DOMAIN your-app.clerk.accounts.dev
